OL,3,COwner of XL bully which mauled
OL,4,CWarrington pensioner gets 12 years in
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FThe owner of an XL Bully has been
OL,8,Fjailed for 12 years after his dog
OL,9,Fsavaged and killed an 84-year-old man
OL,10,F"as if he were its prey".
OL,12,FSo: John McColl died from his injuries
OL,13,Fa month after the attack by the dog,
OL,14,Fcalled Toretto, which weighed seven
OL,15,Fstone four pounds.
OL,17,FThe dog had to be shot 10 times by
OL,18,Farmed police officers who were called
OL,19,Fto the scene in Warrington, on 24
OL,20,FFebruary 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
