PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776525067
OL,3,COwner of XL bully which mauled
OL,4,CWarrington pensioner gets 12 years in
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FSean Garner, 31, pleaded guilty last
OL,8,Fmonth of possessing the banned male
OL,9,Fdog and a female of the same breed
OL,10,Fwithout an exemption certificate .
OL,12,FHe was then convicted after a trial of
OL,13,Fbeing the owner of a dog which caused
OL,14,Finjury while dangerously out of
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,FA trial heard the attack happened
OL,18,Fafter Mr McColl wandered onto the
OL,19,Fdriveway of Garner's property in
OL,20,FBardsley Avenue, at about 6pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
