OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776525067
OL,3,COwner of XL bully which mauled
OL,4,CWarrington pensioner gets 12 years in
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FThe dog had been left on a patio area
OL,8,Fwhich the prosecution alleged was only
OL,9,Fsecured by a gate with a latch.
OL,11,FA member of the public heard Mr McColl
OL,12,Fscreaming for help, and neighbours
OL,13,Fdescribed using items including a
OL,14,Fspirit level and a walking stick to
OL,15,Ftry and get the dog away from Mr
OL,16,FMcColl, a widowed dad-of-three and
OL,17,Fgrandfather.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
