FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776525067
OL,3,COwner of XL bully which mauled
OL,4,CWarrington pensioner gets 12 years in
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FAddressing Garner in court, Mr
OL,8,FMcColl's granddaughter Kelly Percival,
OL,9,F33, said: "Your dog basically ate my
OL,10,Fgrandad, but you and your family don't
OL,11,Fcare."
OL,13,FGarner, 31, looked down as Ms Percival
OL,14,Fread a statement, in which she said he
OL,15,Fhad denied her grandfather a
OL,16,F"dignified death".
OL,18,FMr McColl's daughter, Joann Percival,
OL,19,F57, told the defendant: "You robbed us
OL,20,Fof our dad, grandad, great-grandad,
OL,21,Fbut you don't care and it's not OK."
OL,26,@qD@KOUsD@FO]xD@AOUxD@QO]{D@YOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
