PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776525067
OL,3,COwner of XL bully which mauled
OL,4,CWarrington pensioner gets 12 years in
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FJailing Garner, Judge Brian Cummings
OL,8,FKC said: "The suffering experienced by
OL,9,FMr McColl was quite unspeakable and
OL,10,Freally does not bear dwelling on."
OL,12,FHe said the retired steel erector, who
OL,13,Fremained conscious throughout the
OL,14,Fattack, must have been in "absolute
OL,15,Fagony".
OL,17,FGarner has previous convictions for
OL,18,Fdriving and drugs offences, the court
OL,19,Fwas told.
OL,26,@pD@JOUrD@bO]vD@[OUwD@FO]
